  <brief_title>Study the Signs of Ocular Degeneration in a Population Cohort (Dijon 3C Montrachet Cohort)</brief_title>
  <acronym>3C</acronym>
  <official_title>Study the Signs of Ocular Degeneration in a Population Cohort (Dijon 3C Montrachet Cohort): Seek Correlations Between Signs of Neurological and Vascular Degeneration and Signs of Ocular Aging</official_title>
  <sponsors>
